# ✅ Best Practices:
# 1. Use Azure Key Vault for production secrets
# 2. Rotate tokens regularly (every 90 days)
# 3. Use service principals instead of personal tokens when possible
# 4. Limit token scopes to minimum required
# 5. Use separate credentials for dev/test/prod environments

